title: T H E CAT 101 To Kill a Priest
description:
T.H.E. Cat 101 - To Kill a Priest (16 Sep 1966)

"Out of the night comes a man who saves lives at the risk of his own. Once a circus performer, an aerialist who refused the net... once a cat burglar, a master among jewel thieves... and now, a professional bodyguard, primitive, savage, in love with danger : T.H.E CAT!" In this episode, Cat feels that the police protection being given to a waterfront priest is not enough to save him from racketeers who wish to kill him.

Stars:
Robert Loggia as Thomas Hewitt Edward Cat
R.G. Armstrong as Captain MacAllister
Robert Carricut as Pepe Cordoza

Guest Stars:
Norma Bengell as Maria
Jason Evers as The Priest
Sorrell Booke as Mr. Smith
Roy Jenson as Slavic
Wilhelm Von Homburg as Tony
Jack Perkins as Fisherman 1
George Keymas as Scarface

Writer: Harry Julian Fink
Director: Boris Sagal

Note: This is an unaired version of the pilot that is 5 minutes longer than the aired version.
